rows.label: tlk44310182_02_msg0001
rows.name:
You guys are the worst...
Doctors say it'll take me ten days
to recover from your attacks.

rows.label: tlk44310182_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Kidding, kidding! There's no hard
feelings, really. I should've been
made of stronger stuff.

rows.label: tlk44310182_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Yeah, I'm actually rather embarrassed
for myself, so confident that you could
never take me on...

rows.label: tlk44310182_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But at least now I know my weakness,
so I can adjust my training regimen to
compensate, like a good soldier!
